        <abstract> 
<p>"The number of worms in your garden is astonishing … it will be an interesting observation, how soon the land is again stocked with worms, &amp; whether the grass grows better before this happens.<ref target="#foot.f1"/> – I neglected to observe whether worms distruct [disturb?] the roots of grasses. – You will probably be able to borrow … my book <hi rend="italic">On the Formation of Vegetable Mould</hi> … in which … you will find a good deal about the natural history of worms."</p> 
        </abstract>
